{"tid":1576463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全民CCTV 阻止被自殺再出現","createTime":"2019-09-17T09:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T14:12:11.000Z","uid":1410,"like":60,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"a424e8521c55eb6c3622bdc3671f22cb92b17bd3","tid":1576463,"uid":1410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:06:17.000Z","msg":"被自殺證據確鑿 有人已經幫我地fact check咗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1575614\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1575614</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n跟據上面位巴打個post，8月中打後自殺個案急升<br />\n數據顯示極唔尋常，有好大可能被自殺後黑警毀屍滅跡<br />\n<br />\n當中多個個案都係跳樓自殺，而且現場並無巨響，出現唔合常理嘅靜音跳樓<br />\n<br />\n為咗阻止再有類似案件發生，我提議<span style=\"color: red;\">全民裝CCTV攝錄樓下嘅影像同聲音</span><br />\n<br />\n現階段我地無真憑實據去指控黑警，唯有試下依個方法，若果大家有咩意見，一齊提出討論<br />\n真係唔想再有手足被自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我好希望所有猜測都係炒車，無一個手足被自殺，但情況已經愈嚟愈嚴重，如果冷處理只會有更多同類事件發生"},{"pid":"8bf7877187cb60e9451b67ff5309f8b083693aee","tid":1576463,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:06:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【922攻略流出】<br />\n907<span style=\"color: gold;\">加強版</span>配合hkmap live <br />\n更「大局」交通測試，彩虹戰衣、影帝、機巴、塞鐵、嶄新突擊RB、私家車傾巢而出，裡應外合 <br />\n+機場員工集體Call Sick <br />\n+雷達站/機場附近新搞作<br />\n+大量中港貨櫃司機加入物資支援！<br />\n<br />\n更多攻略，陸續公布，敬請留意"},{"pid":"b8dcecb0c23cf4579c7d784f5130e8d8567347ce","tid":1576463,"uid":1410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:06:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd51cb2a0